Package: rocky
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9)
Recommends: python3-yaml
Maintainer: Rocky project <rocky@localhost>
Description: Typed control layer for a local Debian LLM
 Rocky sits between a local LLM and Debian. The LLM proposes typed actions.
 A policy layer approves or refuses them. An executor runs only approved
 actions as argv arrays, never through a shell. An audit log records every
 action, decision, command, and result to SQLite.
